  <brief_title>The Illness of Uncertainty, Personality and Coping Strategies in Patients With Hepatocellular Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Illness of Uncertainty, Personality and Coping Strategies in Patients With Hepatocellular Carcinoma</official_title>
