  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aims of this study are to (1) understand the uncertainty , personality and coping
      strategies in patients with HCC, and identify the significant factors for coping.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A cross-sectional correlated design will be used and (2) patients will be recruited by
      purposive sampling from wards and outpatient departments at a medical center in Taipei.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
